e8d37758-69b7-4225-8220-cbe014bbe7d2.text:
I'll want 875 coins to let you enter; this is a dungeon
for the more wealthy discerning adventurer. Begone
with you, riff raff.

e925fd83-8b38-458f-b724-3fbee96a7b2d.title: <player>
e925fd83-8b38-458f-b724-3fbee96a7b2d.text: Can I pay you for permanent access?

a37d6b48-263a-4044-af02-66a91020ae7c.title: Saniboch
a37d6b48-263a-4044-af02-66a91020ae7c.text:
I suppose so, yes. My employer will let you in for free,
forever, in exchange for 1,000,000 coins.

options.text: Okay, here's 1,000,000 coins.
Never mind.

d5c1e98e-b216-48a2-9697-d55434b5c5ca.text:
You give Saniboch 1,000,000 coins for permanent
access to the dungeon.

e6a47ba2-3472-47e1-93b0-c4af6fcd1ff3.text:
Many thanks. You may now pass the door as many
times as you wish, and I will not charge you again.
May your death be a glorious one!

15abe100-b3f3-409f-b34e-96c573c63f09.text:

coins.

strange dogs. Adventurers come from all around to
explore its depths.
